public static record CommandDefinition.CommandConfig(@NotNull InteractionContextType[] context, @NotNull IntegrationType[] integration, @NotNull CommandScope scope, boolean isNSFW, @NotNull Permission[] enabledPermissions) extends Record
Stores the configuration values for registering commands. This acts as a representation of CommandConfig
